Dictionaries
-------------
Dictionaries are unordered key-value pairs
dict = {'key1':'value1', 'key2':'value2'}
e.g.,
dp =
{'apple': 100,
 'banana': 5,
 'veg': {'carrot': 10, 'bean': 20},
 'count': [1, 2, 3]}
dp['apple']												10
dp['veg']['carrot']										10

