eggs(spam)
print(spam) ------>[1, 2, 3, 'Hello']

To have a copy of a list

import copy
spam=[1,2,3]
cheese = copy.deepcopy(spam)
cheese[0]=0
print(cheese)
[0, 2, 3]
print(spam)
[1, 2, 3]

