You can save variables in your Python programs to binary shelf files using the shelve module

import shelve
shelfile = shelve.open('mydata')
shelfile['cats'] = ['puss', 'pussy', 'pussycat']
list(shelfile.keys())
['cats']
list(shelfile.values())
[['puss', 'pussy', 'pussycat']]
shelfile.close()

